'''Olyvar''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 3|third]], [[Season 4|fourth]], and [[Season 5|fifth]] seasons. He is played by guest star [[Will Tudor]], and debuts in &quot;[[Kissed by Fire]]&quot;. Olyvar is a spy and a [[Prostitution|prostitute]], specializing in homosexual relations, in the employ of [[Petyr Baelish|Petyr &quot;Littlefinger&quot; Baelish]].

